<headline>Special Weather Statement issued January 07 at 12:59PM EST  by NWS New York City - Upton</headline>
<description>Moderate to locally heavy snow showers are reducing visibilities
across eastern Long Island. With temperatures near the freezing
mark, slick spots may develop on any untreated surfaces. Use extra
caution should be used if traveling this afternoon.</description>
